{
  "texts": [
    "Now, causal machine learning is gaining traction with recent work leveraging causal inference methods 79 to predict displacement in Somalia 80, providing insights for humanitarian response and planning.",
    "Furthermore, symbolic regression is used to discover symbolic expressions directly from data, allowing for interpretatability [81] [82] [83] [84].",
    "Looking ahead, transformers, like the Perceiver-IO 85 and 4M 86 models, show promise in handling multiple modalities and long-range teleconnections.",
    "These models can combine diverse data, such as county-level agricultural data and high-resolution satellite imagery, for applications like crop yield prediction 87.",
    "Transformers also demonstrate success in leveraging circulation-driven teleconnections to forecast global wildfire risk 70, paving the way for improved EWS leveraging similar cross-boundary effects such as supply chains or streamflow."
  ]
}